A few quotes from the article:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Many southerners say the flag honors the memory of their ancestors who fought and died for the south.<br>
<br>
But the Confederacy wasn't just about southern independence. It also vigorously defended slavery.<br>
